---
title: Observatory System Architecture
---
graph TB
    subgraph Internet
        User((User))
    end

    subgraph K3s Cluster
        Traefik[Traefik\nIngress + TLS]

        subgraph observatory namespace
            GW[api-gateway\n:8080]
            AUTH[auth-svc\n:8081]
            USR[user-svc\n:8082]
            ALERT[alert-svc\n:8083]
            NOTIFY[notify-svc\n:8084]
            INC[incident-svc\n:8085]
        end

        subgraph observatory-data namespace
            NATS[(NATS\nJetStream)]
            PG1[(PostgreSQL\nuser-svc)]
            PG2[(PostgreSQL\nalert-svc)]
            PG3[(PostgreSQL\nincident-svc)]
            REDIS[(Redis\nauth + alert)]
        end

        subgraph monitoring namespace
            PROM[Prometheus]
        end
    end

    subgraph External
        SLACK[Slack]
        LETSENCRYPT[Let's Encrypt]
    end

    User -->|HTTPS| Traefik
    Traefik --> GW
    GW -->|validate token| AUTH
    GW -->|REST| USR
    GW -->|REST| ALERT
    GW -->|REST| INC

    AUTH --- REDIS
    USR --- PG1
    ALERT --- PG2
    ALERT --- REDIS
    INC --- PG3

    ALERT -->|poll metrics| PROM
    ALERT -->|alert.fired\nalert.resolved| NATS
    USR -->|user.created| NATS
    NATS -->|consume| NOTIFY
    NATS -->|consume| INC

    NOTIFY -->|send| SLACK
    Traefik -.->|ACME| LETSENCRYPT
